  "short_description": "Become a giant dinosaur and flatten entire cities before the City Defenders can stop you! Crumbling City is chaos and fun in a physics based destructible world. Rampage across cities as a colossal dinosaur and leave nothing standing! Nature’s revenge has never been this fun!",
